{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects/task-13","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i odgovori na pitanje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects/task-13"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Prema razgovoru, koja rečenica pokazuje ispravnu upotrebu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going to</span> prema trenutnim dokazima?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We will probably use React since it's a popular choice these days.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova rečenica koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">will</span> za akciju koja bi mogla da se dogodi kasnije, a koja ne odražava odluku donetu na osnovu trenutnih dokaza.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I think we will go with Node.js for the back-end, considering our team's expertise.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">will</span> se koristi za buduću akciju prema trenutnom stanju, ali <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going to</span> bi bio precizniji jer odluka izgleda zavisiti od trenutne stručnosti tima.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We're going to need a UX designer because the project is complex.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I will call the designer since we're going to need one for this project.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova rečenica koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">will</span> za naglu odluku (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">calling the designer</span>), koja je tačna, ali ne pokazuje upotrebu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">going to</span> prema trenutnim dokazima.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null},{"character":"Brian","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null}],"audio":{"filename":"8.2-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":null,"finishTimestamp":null},"alwaysShowDialogue":true},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":{"x":70,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":0.5,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":4.52,"dialogue":{"text":"Brian, it's time to discuss our plans for the upcoming project.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.36,"finishTime":6.7,"dialogue":{"text":"What do you think we should do?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.26,"finishTime":10.9,"dialogue":{"text":"Well, we're going to use a framework for the front-end, probably React.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.16,"finishTime":15.02,"dialogue":{"text":"It's the technology we're most comfortable with and it will make development faster.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":15.56,"finishTime":20.3,"dialogue":{"text":"Good point. I agree. I also think we are going to need a dedicated UX designer.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.68,"finishTime":25.3,"dialogue":{"text":"It's a complex project and a professional designer will help us create a great user interface.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":26,"finishTime":29.3,"dialogue":{"text":"Absolutely. And as for the back-end, I think we'll use Node.js.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":29.3,"finishTime":33.36,"dialogue":{"text":"It's a solid choice and it will allow us to scale the application effectively.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":34.44,"finishTime":36.36,"dialogue":{"text":"Sure thing. I'm glad we're on the same page.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":36.8,"finishTime":39.36,"dialogue":{"text":"Let's finalize these plans and start assigning tasks.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Brian","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":39.86,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":40.36,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Lekcija 13","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects","dashedName":"task-13","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-updates-and-plans-for-tasks-and-projects/task-14","prevChallen